Application prerequisite
========================
Java : 1.8
Maven : 3.3.9
MySQL Server : 5.7

Configuration
==============
Go to application.properties file and edit following properties
spring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/notes?createDatabaseIfNotExist=true&useSSL=false
spring.datasource.username=root
spring.datasource.password=1234

Tomcat server port can be change by following
server.port=8082

How to run application
=======================
Go to project root and run 'mvn clean spring-boot:run"
Open the browser and go to 'http://localhost:8082/add_note.html'

Log Details
=============
Root logging level set to INFO level
All the logs write to 'note.log' file which is located under project root.